{"tid":1603244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線手足必入，關於卧底","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:07:25.000Z","uid":306842,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6012c77d00f5befa300285375135a09c3f70d7aa","tid":1603244,"uid":306842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"今日唔知係邊度睇到條片，見到有班喬裝狗會合軍裝狗嘅時候只係講咗一聲「自己人」，啲狗即刻信晒佢哋，check都冇check就即刻幫佢做掩護。假如有一日手足們俾狗拉嘅時候可唔可以試吓講句「自己人」，然後趁班狗仲未反應得切嘅時候，喺呢一個時間跑走？<br />\n我見果班喬裝狗連普通暗號都冇做，所以我覺得抵得諗。與其咁順攤俾人拉，咁不如博一博。<br />\n含撚啦Mon po 狗，道高一尺魔高一丈啊柒頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:冷氣撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6caf5a6a13667dc396e5e70cd1224bfe8b7f79","tid":1603244,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa05c9d4479734d2ff151a7f894173ec505e00d5","tid":1603244,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f35e59675c4eff0e493de71d5e3e389c52a3af","tid":1603244,"uid":306842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"321e580a0e98a9467c5a288be785554f08063456","tid":1603244,"uid":306842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d6caf5a6a13667dc396e5e70cd1224bfe8b7f79","tid":1603244,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"啲片唔見有"},{"pid":"a644af56ce1d2d4c82af26246cd5041656330302","tid":1603244,"uid":306842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa05c9d4479734d2ff151a7f894173ec505e00d5","tid":1603244,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite